import Polygons.DataStructures
import Polygons.EvenGraphDecompositionImpl
import Polygons.RayIntersectionAlgorithmImpl

namespace MultipolygonIntersectionAlgorithmImpl

/-!
# Multipolygon intersection algorithm — computable layer

The 18 runtime `def`s the algorithm evaluates, lifted out of
`Polygons.MultipolygonIntersectionAlgorithmProofs` so the WASM build can
initialise this module alone (and DCE every theorem-only initialiser
the proof file pulls in).

Each `def` here is the *exact* definition the proof file's theorems are
about; there is no duplication. The proof file imports this Compute
